Comment (src/views/admin/NotificationsView.vue:1406):
The custom tab implementation uses `role="tablist"`/`role="tab"`, but the tabs are missing the required relationships for accessible ARIA tabs (e.g., each tab should have an `id` and `aria-controls` pointing at a corresponding panel, and each panel should have `role="tabpanel"` + an `id` and `aria-labelledby`). Consider switching to the existing `@/volt/Tabs.vue` / `TabList` / `Tab` components used elsewhere in the repo, or add the missing ARIA attributes + keyboard handling.
